item.title: Sopranos finale
item.dc:creator: Brian Kirsten
item.content:encoded: As if enough people aren't talking about it. I spent the couple minutes between the Sopranos finale and John From Cincinnati yelling "That's how they ended Sopranos?" at the TV. And I'm intrigued enough about John From Cincinnati to give it a couple of episodes.
